<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=99719277340337></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f99719277340337><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=item.html?item=3883&mid=99719277340337>RE: Decisions</a> <a id=fs8 href=item.html?item=3883&mid=99719277340337#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=24929><span id= >Willough</span></a>, <span id= > </span><br><span id=notbold>16 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Tue, Aug 7th 9:59 AM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Chipped Velium Amulet&nbsp;&nbsp; AC: +4 Str: +4 HP: +30  wt 0.1<br>Orc Fang Necklace  +5 AC +3 Strength +3 Stamina +3 Agility  wt 1.0  <br>     The Orc Fang is superior in AC.  As a warrior I'd go with the orc fang, especially if your stamina is below 100.  Avoiding one hit with the extra point of AC is more important than the 30 HPs; I think eeven the bunnies in Eastern Wastes hit for 30.  When your STA is above 100, you don't get stat penalties for being out of stamina.  Monks may opt for the CVA to avoid the Orc Fang's weight.<br>     If you are a warrior having encumbrance problems, the CVA may be the better choice because it offers more strength at much less weight to keep you agile longer.  You don't want to use a full point of STR just to wear the Orc Fang when trying to solve the encumbrance issue.<br>     AC is king.  One less point of AC to solve an encumberance problem is one way to maintain your AC once the loot begins to pile up.  <br><br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
	   <span style='font-weight: normal; font-size: 9px;'>[<a href=#top>Top</a>]</span></tr>
	   </form></table><ul>
<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=99907966112619></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f99907966112619><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=item.html?item=3883&mid=99907966112619>RE: Decisions</a> <a id=fs8 href=item.html?item=3883&mid=99907966112619#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=71614><span id= >Eitsekur</span></a>, <span id= > </span><br><span id=notbold>99 posts</td></tr>
