	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[2.50]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>As an alternative to either the Orc Fang or the Chipped Velium, I would highly recommend a Ry'gorr collar, which has a 9ac (much better than either of these).&nbsp;&nbsp;As a warrior, AC is be king (well, saves are regarded most highly as king as I am sure someone would mention at some point).  The str of an item should never become a deciding factor over the AC on an item when the difference is this great, and when the stats on a Ry'gorr collar are still quite good.<br><br>Eitsekur Eitfyndir<br>28 Shadow Knight (Erudite)<br>Heartbinder's Heroes, 7th Hammer<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
